sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Flutter екран
    participant MM as ModelManager
    participant SDK as EdgeVeda
    participant RT as Нативний runtime

    UI->>MM: downloadModel(ModelRegistry.llama32_1b)
    MM-->>UI: modelPath
    UI->>SDK: init(EdgeVedaConfig)
    SDK->>RT: завантажити модель
    UI->>SDK: generateStream(prompt)
    SDK-->>UI: фрагменти токенів
    UI->>SDK: dispose()
